name: ViacoinPrice
0:
”Alexa, open Viacoin Price”
”Alexa, ask Viacoin Price for the Viacoin Price”
”Alexa, ask Viacoin Price, What is the Viacoin Price?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: viacoin price
des:
Using Viacoin Price, you can translate receive an up to date price of Viacoin.

To open Viacoin Price say:
'Alexa, open Viacoin Price'
Once there say: 'What is the Viacoin price?'
To ask for the skill without opening it, say: 'Alexa, ask Viacoin Price for the Viacoin price'
